strings: <se_def>*: ...that's why you're here! And go after it! I think this time it's my turn to tell my story...
<se_def>*: Dolmago killed our leader, Lord Gilding, and he must be avenged.
<se_def>*: He's trapped in the bin. So we continue...
<se_def>*: It was dark and you could see nothing. There was nothing for us to do but withdraw. Seems we've come too far.
<se_def>*: I certainly have. But even if the black spirit still exists, I can't get near it.
<se_def>*: Come up with a solution. Look at Emperor Aljun's mirror.
<se_def>*: There seems to be a magic mirror in the Wurm family tree that can reverse the darkness. this can be helpful
<se_def>*: However, I highly doubt they will lend us the money. If you owe us anything
